manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Five Star Stay-Put Pocket & Prong Folder Neatly organize all your papers including class notes, homework assignments and class handouts in this Stay-Put Pocket and Prong Paper Folder. Folder has two horizontal pockets and stay-put tabs let you tuck in the page corners so the papers don't move while in the folder. The three prongs keep hole punched papers in place. Take the durable folder between classes and back and forth from school to home without worry. Durable one-piece construction lasts all year Three prongs to hold hole punched paper Includes 2 pockets with stay-put tab Three prongs Pocket for index cards

Stay-Put Design This two pocket folder provides better paper security with stay-put tabs. Place papers in the horizontal pockets and tuck the top corners into the tabs to keep the papers neatly in place. Classic 3 prong design provides excellent paper security for all your hole punched sheets. Serves as a slim, stylish alternative to a 3 ring binder.

Five Star Folder Multipack Five Star Sewn Binder Five Star Multipack Notebooks You may also be interested in: Two durable vertical and horizontal storage pockets Durable and Water Resistant 2-Inch Zipper Binder 1 subject notebook with 100 wide ruled, 3 hole punched sheet

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My kid’s teachers always make them a homework folder and I always immediately replace it with these. They last the whole year and keep all the papers from getting demolished in the bag with a cheap folder.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They never fail!
reviews.reviewText: Love love these folders, I’ve only had to buy 1 or two new ones but that’s bc the teachers wanted a different color, otherwise they don’t need replacing. They are sturdy, don’t rip, hold a great amount of paper. Great investment as far as I’m concerned.

reviews.reviewText: it should be like $2, but its like $3.90. But anyways, great 5-star product. Color is cute af. Sturdy and holds a lot of papers.
